FSync no
MaxMessages 200
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User azuwis@gmail.com
UseIMAPS yes
PassCmd "pass show email/azuwis@gmail.com"

IMAPStore gmail
Account gmail

MaildirStore local
Path ~/Maildir/
Inbox ~/Maildir/inbox/

Channel gmail-inbox
Master :gmail:
Slave :local:

Channel gmail-corp
Master :gmail:corp
Slave :local:corp

Channel gmail-sent
Master :gmail:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :local:sent
MaxMessages 100

Channel gmail-drafts
Master :gmail:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :local:drafts
MaxMessages 100

Channel gmail-trash
Master :gmail:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :local:trash
MaxMessages 50

# Channel gmail-test
# Master :gmail:
# Slave :local:
# Patterns *

Group gmail
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-corp
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-trash
